Meal plans are there for inspo. I actually tell my clients not to follow them to a T. 

If you can only follow a strict diet plan, you’re not learning how to adapt for meals you like, eating out, when someone else cooks, etc. 

Plus we all have different tastes,  Family size, goals, so it’s not one size fits all. 

Best advice is to meat prep: if you have meat cooked and ready the rest will be so much easier
